Load startup screen with difficulty options and tutorial checkbox checked by default.

IF (TUTORIAL IS CHECKED) {
  Begin tutorial:
  Avatar says she wants to make money by selling cookies.
  Go to stand screen.
  Show customer with 1 sugar cookie in thought bubble.
  User clicks desired cookie, and that cookie shows up on the plate?

  Go to profits screen.
  Show predetermined values based on difficulty.
  
  instanciate click variable as false.
  WHILE (CLICK IS FALSE) {
  
    Have the user click on the correct profit bubble.
    
    IF (CLICK IS FALSE) {
      Tell user to try again.
      Warn them.
    }
    
  }
  Give user predetermined money.
}
